 TWO time BET Awards recipient, Burna Boy has spoken on the wonders of the impact of his songs on people around the world. “This song is about the ‘wonders’ of seeing the impact of my music on people’s lives as they shared their joy, pain, and pleasure with me while I toured the world,” he said. The singer made this known as he released the official visual of his new single, ‘Wonderful’. The single which was released few days before his 29th birthday is the first single off his upcoming album, Twice as Tall. In 2019, Burna Boy described his compositions as Afro-fusion while maintaining that he is an African Giant.